        " الْهِنْدَبَاءُ سَيِّدُ الْبُقُولِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Haroun Bin Muslim, from Mas’ada Bin sadaqa, from Ziyad, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The endive is the chief of the vegetables’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "5. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from Harun ibn Muslim from Mas’adah ibn Sadaqah from Ziyad who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘The endive is the master of herbs.’” "
        ]
      }
